{
  "texts": [
    "As shown above, GPT's answer does not directly produce a list of causal elements hence we employ a series of 12 filters to extract them (Table 3).",
    "The list of filters was inspired by the design of earlier prototypes (Davis et al., 2022), which themselves often inherit practices from natural language processing for social media analytics.",
    "The specific filters and their order were determined through trial-and-error.",
    "Filters belong to two broad categories.",
    "Low-level filters involve a few lines of Python code and are guaranteed to work."
  ]
}